[
  {
    "id": 5623,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "77:1",
    "textAr": "وَٱلْمُرْسَلَـٰتِ عُرْفًا",
    "textEn": "By those [winds] sent forth in gusts",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5624,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "77:2",
    "textAr": "فَٱلْعَـٰصِفَـٰتِ عَصْفًا",
    "textEn": "And the winds that blow violently",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5625,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "77:3",
    "textAr": "وَٱلنَّـٰشِرَٰتِ نَشْرًا",
    "textEn": "And [by] the winds that spread [clouds]",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5626,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "77:4",
    "textAr": "فَٱلْفَـٰرِقَـٰتِ فَرْقًا",
    "textEn": "And those [angels] who bring criterion",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5627,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "77:5",
    "textAr": "فَٱلْمُلْقِيَـٰتِ ذِكْرًا",
    "textEn": "And those [angels] who deliver a message.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5628,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "77:6",
    "textAr": "عُذْرًا أَوْ نُذْرًا",
    "textEn": "As justification or warning,",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5629,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "77:7",
    "textAr": "إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٌ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, what you are promised is to occur.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5630,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "77:8",
    "textAr": "فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتْ",
    "textEn": "So when the stars are obliterated",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5631,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "77:9",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the heaven is opened",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5632,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "77:10",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْجِبَالُ نُسِفَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the mountains are blown away",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5633,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "77:11",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the messengers' time has come...",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5634,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "77:12",
    "textAr": "لِأَىِّ يَوْمٍ أُجِّلَتْ",
    "textEn": "For what Day was it postponed?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5635,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "77:13",
    "textAr": "لِيَوْمِ ٱلْفَصْلِ",
    "textEn": "For the Day of Judgement.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5636,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "77:14",
    "textAr": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلْفَصْلِ",
    "textEn": "And what can make you know what is the Day of Judgement?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5637,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "77:15",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5638,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "77:16",
    "textAr": "أَلَمْ نُهْلِكِ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ",
    "textEn": "Did We not destroy the former peoples?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5639,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "77:17",
    "textAr": "ثُمَّ نُتْبِعُهُمُ ٱلْـَٔاخِرِينَ",
    "textEn": "Then We will follow them with the later ones.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5640,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "77:18",
    "textAr": "كَذَٰلِكَ نَفْعَلُ بِٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ",
    "textEn": "Thus do We deal with the criminals.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5641,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "77:19",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 580,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5642,
    "number": 20,
    "key": "77:20",
    "textAr": "أَلَمْ نَخْلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٍ مَّهِينٍ",
    "textEn": "Did We not create you from a liquid disdained?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5643,
    "number": 21,
    "key": "77:21",
    "textAr": "فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُ فِى قَرَارٍ مَّكِينٍ",
    "textEn": "And We placed it in a firm lodging [i.e., the womb]",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5644,
    "number": 22,
    "key": "77:22",
    "textAr": "إِلَىٰ قَدَرٍ مَّعْلُومٍ",
    "textEn": "For a known extent.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5645,
    "number": 23,
    "key": "77:23",
    "textAr": "فَقَدَرْنَا فَنِعْمَ ٱلْقَـٰدِرُونَ",
    "textEn": "And We determined [it], and excellent [are We] to determine.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5646,
    "number": 24,
    "key": "77:24",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5647,
    "number": 25,
    "key": "77:25",
    "textAr": "أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ ٱلْأَرْضَ كِفَاتًا",
    "textEn": "Have We not made the earth a container",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5648,
    "number": 26,
    "key": "77:26",
    "textAr": "أَحْيَآءً وَأَمْوَٰتًا",
    "textEn": "Of the living and the dead?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5649,
    "number": 27,
    "key": "77:27",
    "textAr": "وَجَعَلْنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِىَ شَـٰمِخَـٰتٍ وَأَسْقَيْنَـٰكُم مَّآءً فُرَاتًا",
    "textEn": "And We placed therein lofty, firmly set mountains and have given you to drink sweet water.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5650,
    "number": 28,
    "key": "77:28",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5651,
    "number": 29,
    "key": "77:29",
    "textAr": "ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ",
    "textEn": "[They will be told], \"Proceed to that which you used to deny.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5652,
    "number": 30,
    "key": "77:30",
    "textAr": "ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰ ظِلٍّ ذِى ثَلَـٰثِ شُعَبٍ",
    "textEn": "Proceed to a shadow [of smoke] having three columns.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5653,
    "number": 31,
    "key": "77:31",
    "textAr": "لَّا ظَلِيلٍ وَلَا يُغْنِى مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ",
    "textEn": "[But having] no cool shade and availing not against the flame.\"",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5654,
    "number": 32,
    "key": "77:32",
    "textAr": "إِنَّهَا تَرْمِى بِشَرَرٍ كَٱلْقَصْرِ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, it throws sparks [as huge] as a fortress,",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5655,
    "number": 33,
    "key": "77:33",
    "textAr": "كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَـٰلَتٌ صُفْرٌ",
    "textEn": "As if they were yellowish [black] camels.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5656,
    "number": 34,
    "key": "77:34",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5657,
    "number": 35,
    "key": "77:35",
    "textAr": "هَـٰذَا يَوْمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ",
    "textEn": "This is a Day they will not speak,",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5658,
    "number": 36,
    "key": "77:36",
    "textAr": "وَلَا يُؤْذَنُ لَهُمْ فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ",
    "textEn": "Nor will it be permitted for them to make an excuse.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5659,
    "number": 37,
    "key": "77:37",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5660,
    "number": 38,
    "key": "77:38",
    "textAr": "هَـٰذَا يَوْمُ ٱلْفَصْلِ ۖ جَمَعْنَـٰكُمْ وَٱلْأَوَّلِينَ",
    "textEn": "This is the Day of Judgement; We will have assembled you and the former peoples.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5661,
    "number": 39,
    "key": "77:39",
    "textAr": "فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمْ كَيْدٌ فَكِيدُونِ",
    "textEn": "So if you have a plan, then plan against Me.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5662,
    "number": 40,
    "key": "77:40",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5663,
    "number": 41,
    "key": "77:41",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ فِى ظِلَـٰلٍ وَعُيُونٍ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, the righteous will be among shades and springs",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5664,
    "number": 42,
    "key": "77:42",
    "textAr": "وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشْتَهُونَ",
    "textEn": "And fruits from whatever they desire,",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5665,
    "number": 43,
    "key": "77:43",
    "textAr": "كُلُوا۟ وَٱشْرَبُوا۟ هَنِيٓـًٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ",
    "textEn": "[Being told], \"Eat and drink in satisfaction for what you used to do.\"",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5666,
    "number": 44,
    "key": "77:44",
    "textAr": "إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5667,
    "number": 45,
    "key": "77:45",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5668,
    "number": 46,
    "key": "77:46",
    "textAr": "كُلُوا۟ وَتَمَتَّعُوا۟ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجْرِمُونَ",
    "textEn": "[O disbelievers], eat and enjoy yourselves a little; indeed, you are criminals.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5669,
    "number": 47,
    "key": "77:47",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5670,
    "number": 48,
    "key": "77:48",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرْكَعُوا۟ لَا يَرْكَعُونَ",
    "textEn": "And when it is said to them, \"Bow [in prayer],\" they do not bow.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5671,
    "number": 49,
    "key": "77:49",
    "textAr": "وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ",
    "textEn": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers.",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  },
  {
    "id": 5672,
    "number": 50,
    "key": "77:50",
    "textAr": "فَبِأَىِّ حَدِيثٍۭ بَعْدَهُۥ يُؤْمِنُونَ",
    "textEn": "Then in what statement after it [i.e., the Qur’ān] will they believe?",
    "juz": 29,
    "page": 581,
    "hizb": 58
  }
]